animeDescription: Music video for the song Sherlock Holmes to Watson Hakase by Kei Tani that was featured on NHK's Minna no Uta program. It is an original Japanese song that pays homage to Arthur Conan Doyle's Sherlock Holmes series. The video was animated by Hal Fukushima.
animeStaff: [['Doyle Arthur Ignatius Conan', ['Original Creator']], ['Fukushima Hal', ['Animation Director']]]
